entries.journal_entry_completion_summary: The Slavemaster lies dead by your hands. The justice you have brought by this act erases any doubts you might have had about taking his life.
entries.journal_entry_description: Anyza has bourne the brunt of a lot of the Slavemaster's depraved sicknesses. She wants revenge. You must find out where the Slavemaster is and kill him.
entries.task00_journal_entry_description: Something terrible drives Anyza to seek revenge. She has asked you to kill the slavemaster of the slave ring.
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: Return to Anyza and let her know the slavemaster is dead.
